JADE

PLOT SUMMARY

Linda Fiorentino plays Trina, a stylish and seductive wife of a San Francisco 
lawyer, who has some unusual bedroom hobbies.  When the assistant district 
attorney of San Francisco investigates the mysterious death of an important 
millionaire he discovers that Trina may be involved. He becomes enthralled with 
her and it becomes difficult for him to distinguish between what is reality and 
what should be reality.

Excellent scenary shots of San Francisco, exciting car chases, great 
soundtrack by Loreena McKennitt, and of course, Linda Fiorentino.
